content: I've definitely noticed that I have more free time in the evening because I'm not spending hours cleaning. And yeah, I'd say I've experienced reduced stress and anxiety too. It's nice to come home to a tidy space after a long day. As for extending my daily cleaning routine, I've actually been doing a deeper clean of the bathroom on Mondays and Thursdays, and I've also been making sure to wipe down the kitchen counters and sink after every meal.
